  "about": {
    "badge": "Built in Herat, Afghanistan",
    "title": "Connecting Afghan Youth to Real Opportunities",
    "subtitle": "KaarYab was built because I got tired of seeing talented young Afghans miss out on opportunities simply because they did not know where to look. Everything in one place. Free. Always.",
