    "problemTitle": "Opportunities exist they are just hard to find",
    "problemDescription": "Jobs, scholarships, internships, and remote work are scattered across dozens of websites, Telegram channels, and Facebook groups. Most young people in Afghanistan miss them not because they are not qualified but because no one told them in time. KaarYab changes that.",
